						<h3>AI Knowledge Base Inclusion</h3>
						<p>Be included in the knowledge bases that generative AI systems learn from. When AI systems learn from your content, you become part of their understanding of your industry and expertise.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>ChatGPT and Claude Citations</h3>
						<p>Get cited when ChatGPT, Claude, and other generative AI systems generate responses. Citations provide visibility and authority even when users don't click through to your website.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Long-Term Authority Building</h3>
						<p>Build authority in AI knowledge bases that persists over time. Unlike traditional SEO rankings that can fluctuate, authority in AI knowledge bases is more stable and long-lasting.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>Future-Proof Content Strategy</h3>
						<p>Prepare for the future of search as generative AI becomes the primary search interface. GEO ensures your content remains discoverable as search evolves toward AI-driven systems.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
						<h3>AI Agent Discoverability</h3>
						<p>Optimize for AI agents and autonomous systems that search the web. As AI agents become more common, GEO ensures your content is discoverable and usable by these systems.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="benefit-item">
