							<p>Content optimized for GEO should be comprehensive and authoritative, provide rich semantic meaning and context, establish clear expertise signals, use consistent formatting that AI systems can learn from, include proper citations and attribution, and cover topics in depth rather than superficially. The goal is to create content that AI systems want to learn from and cite.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-6">
							<span>Can GEO work for any industry?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
