							<p>Yes, GEO can work for any industry. Any business that wants to be discovered and cited by generative AI systems can benefit from GEO. However, industries with high informational content needs (like technology, healthcare, finance, education, and consulting) often see particularly strong results from GEO optimization.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

